divs: Sighting Detailsi was on my way to walmart in sun prairie on saturday night headed west on hwy 19..i was driving and to my right ahead i noticed lights..they were low to the ground. there are lots of farms in the area...i wondered what it was...thought it might be a helicopter..then as i drove it appeared to be in the south...then there were a bunch of trees i had to pass ...i cant remember how long it took me but anyway when i got past the trees the light was gone there wasnt even a spot of light in the sky its like it vanished or landed in one of the cornfields nearby. this is the 8th ufo i have seen i was not scared...i am having a rally in dc to stop the coverup of ufos and aliens by the gov in july and wonder if i will be seeing alot because of it..i have been abducted by the nordics since age 7 when i saw my first ufo
